    <p class="srcnote">Sources for this section: <a href="https://www.ine.mx/voto-y-elecciones/calendario-electoral/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">INE</a> (electoral calendar &amp; results) · <a href="https://www.as-coa.org/articles/approval-tracker-mexicos-president-claudia-sheinbaum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AS/COA Approval Tracker</a> (Mitofsky · AtlasIntel) · <a href="https://www.diputados.gob.mx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cámara de Diputados</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.gob.mx/presidencia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Presidencia</a> (composition, the Informe). Each fact above carries its date and links to the source listed here.</p>
